name: Soul Blossoms Minky Baby Blanket
description:
This is a beautiful blanket great for covering up your little one. On one side of the blanket you have Amy Butler fabric from her Soul Blossoms collection and on the other an incredibly soft minky fabric. This is a handmade blanket using the softest fabrics to create a wonderfully snuggly blanket for you baby. It also makes a lovely gift for a lucky expecting mother.

Made in a smoke free and pet free home. Top stitched for durability.

name: Zoology Sea Car Seat Cover
description:
This is an adorable Michael Miller Zoology Sea print car seat cover, perfect for keeping babies cozy and warm. It has velcro straps to keep it secure. It has rounded corners and has been top-stitched for a finished look. The beautiful combination of colors makes it precious and fashionable. This is a great gift for that baby-shower you are attending! The flannel fabric is beautiful for a baby Boy. 

The car seat cover measures approximately 38”x 34.5” big enough to cover the entire car seat.

Items are ready to ship.

All items are handmade in a smoke and pet free home.
